{"tid":844990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要番工，去創業。","createTime":"2018-10-02T10:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T12:22:43.000Z","uid":71568,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4221c40142e2598d50d12fa61a75111f43467419","tid":844990,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"不要番工，去創業。人生沒有那麼多時間給你打牛工。有興趣就去鑽研佢，喜歡就去創業。朝九晚五有咩用咪又係買唔起樓。唔成功就黎過，冇錢就番part time/一路番工一路搞自己生意。大不了咬老綜，你連第一步都不敢踏出還好意思話自己好唔想幫人地打工，想追夢。繼續浪費人生打呢份自己毫無興趣既工等於繼續社會強姦，強姦到開始懷疑自己的人生，令自己覺得人生的意義就是幫老細完成人地既夢想。"},{"pid":"4618579a8b65b9f4014cd77aab8d77bcb0fc1d50","tid":844990,"uid":34444,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"不要創業，去重新投胎。"},{"pid":"fc5e486bddcce8deada7a8b5b20944b2ecbdf685","tid":844990,"uid":121261,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:12:16.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"6cd9627a66a25cdbfc78d65aeed3d57c9611a55f","tid":844990,"uid":71568,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4618579a8b65b9f4014cd77aab8d77bcb0fc1d50","tid":844990,"uid":34444,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"不要創業，去重新投胎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"正能量post唔講呢d"},{"pid":"492d51d15fa9e3d11e730b994b846c61c6c3850d","tid":844990,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644ed9e089f805e41fbda6d37e000207bdda2015","tid":844990,"uid":186087,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"態度正確<br />\n我都覺打工係幫人完成夢想<br />\n無奈, 創業要數百萬本錢。唔係做part time 可以搵到"},{"pid":"8346bf5b6480c6b10378f9b5e25a2b2796752368","tid":844990,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"644ed9e089f805e41fbda6d37e000207bdda2015","tid":844990,"uid":186087,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:28:18.000Z","m